	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-133363" number="36498" version="2237">
			<HEADING>Chapter 61: Public Hearings Held Pursuant to Administrative Code § 24-110</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17548" name="T15C061"/>Chapter 61: Public Hearings Held Pursuant to Administrative Code § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="24-110" destination-id="0-0-0-0">24-110</LINK>
			</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-133364" number="36499" version="2237">
								<HEADING>§ 61-01 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17550" name="T15C061_61-01"/>§ 61-01 Definitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133377" number="36500" version="2237">
									<PARA>For the purposes of this chapter, the following terms have the following meanings: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133376" number="36501" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Commissioner.</CHARFORMAT> The term &quot;commissioner&quot; means the commissioner of the department, or his or her designee. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133375" number="36502" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Department.</CHARFORMAT> The term &quot;department&quot; means the department of environmental protection. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133374" number="36503" version="2237">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/1/2022, eff. 7/1/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-133378" number="36504" version="2237">
								<HEADING>§ 61-02 Public Hearing Procedures.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17552" name="T15C061_61-02"/>§ 61-02 Public Hearing Procedures.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133373" number="36505" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>a.<TAB tab-count="1"/>If a person files a written objection to a variance petition within twenty-one days from the department&apos;s publication of a notice pursuant to subdivision (c) of § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="24-110" destination-id="0-0-0-0">24-110</LINK> of the Administrative Code or if the commissioner determines that a public hearing regarding such variance petition would be advisable, the department shall hold a public hearing regarding such variance petition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133372" number="36506" version="2237">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>b.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The department shall post a notice regarding each variance petition public hearing on its website. The following information shall be included in each notice: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133371" number="36507" version="2237">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The date and time of the hearing; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133370" number="36508" version="2237">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The subject matter of the hearing, including a brief summary of the variance petition; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133369" number="36509" version="2237">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Information regarding how to appear at the hearing, either in person or by remote means; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133368" number="36510" version="2237">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>4.<TAB tab-count="1"/>Information regarding how written comments can be submitted. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-133367" number="36511" version="2237">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>c.<TAB tab-count="1"/>For a variance petition for which such a public hearing is held, the commissioner shall consider all comments received at such hearing and submitted in writing prior to such hearing before making a decision regarding whether to grant such variance. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-144444" number="36512" version="2627">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/1/2022, eff. 7/1/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-074]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
